
The first thing to do is to activate the virtualenv

workon pelican-blog

Then, use fabric to preview or publish

fab publish

As long as you have ssh-agent forwarding on, it should forward the auth from the laptop to the linux vm, and then onward to NearlyFreeSpeech.net.

Here are the available Fabric commands:

    build
    cf_upload
    clean
    preview
    publish
    rebuild
    regenerate
    reserve
    serve

